---
title: BeaconLink Relay Network State Machine
---

stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    %% =====================================================
    %% Relay Startup
    %% =====================================================

    [*] --> Starting

    Starting : Initialize Relay Service
    Starting : Load Configuration
    Starting : Initialize Networking
    Starting : Load Trust Store

    Starting --> Initializing

    Initializing : Initialize Connection Pools
    Initializing : Initialize Routing Engine
    Initializing : Initialize Session Manager
    Initializing : Initialize Metrics

    Initializing --> Ready

    %% =====================================================
    %% Operational States
    %% =====================================================

    state Ready {

        [*] --> Listening

        Listening : Await Agent Connections
        Listening : Await Control Plane Requests

        Listening --> Authenticating : Incoming Connection
        Listening --> Forwarding : Existing Session
        Listening --> Maintenance : Maintenance Mode

        %% -------------------------------------------------
        %% Authentication
        %% -------------------------------------------------

        Authenticating : Mutual TLS Handshake
        Authenticating : Certificate Validation
        Authenticating : Identity Verification

        Authenticating --> SessionEstablished : Authentication Successful
        Authenticating --> ConnectionRejected : Authentication Failed

        ConnectionRejected : Reject Connection
        ConnectionRejected : Log Security Event

        ConnectionRejected --> Listening

        %% -------------------------------------------------
        %% Session Lifecycle
        %% -------------------------------------------------

        SessionEstablished : Create Secure Session
        SessionEstablished : Allocate Resources
        SessionEstablished : Register Session

        SessionEstablished --> Forwarding

        %% -------------------------------------------------
        %% Traffic Forwarding
        %% -------------------------------------------------

        Forwarding : Forward Control Messages
        Forwarding : Forward Heartbeats
        Forwarding : Forward Deployment Traffic
        Forwarding : Forward Event Streams

        Forwarding --> Routing : Message Received
        Forwarding --> Monitoring : Periodic Health Check
        Forwarding --> SessionExpired : Session Timeout

        Routing : Resolve Destination
        Routing : Apply Routing Policy
        Routing : Select Relay Path

        Routing --> Forwarding : Route Established
        Routing --> RetryRouting : Route Unavailable

        RetryRouting : Retry Alternative Route

        RetryRouting --> Routing
        RetryRouting --> Degraded : Retry Limit Exceeded

        %% -------------------------------------------------
        %% Monitoring
        %% -------------------------------------------------

        Monitoring : Verify Session Health
        Monitoring : Verify Relay Health
        Monitoring : Update Metrics

        Monitoring --> Forwarding : Healthy
        Monitoring --> Degraded : Health Warning

        %% -------------------------------------------------
        %% Maintenance
        %% -------------------------------------------------

        Maintenance : Reject New Sessions
        Maintenance : Drain Existing Sessions

        Maintenance --> Listening : Maintenance Complete

        %% -------------------------------------------------
        %% Degraded
        %% -------------------------------------------------

        Degraded : Limited Routing Capacity
        Degraded : Increased Latency
        Degraded : Partial Availability

        Degraded --> Forwarding : Capacity Restored
        Degraded --> Failed : Critical Failure

        %% -------------------------------------------------
        %% Session Cleanup
        %% -------------------------------------------------

        SessionExpired : Remove Session
        SessionExpired : Release Resources

        SessionExpired --> Listening

    }

    %% =====================================================
    %% Federation States
    %% =====================================================

    state Federation {

        [*] --> DiscoverPeers

        DiscoverPeers : Discover Relay Peers

        DiscoverPeers --> Synchronizing

        Synchronizing : Exchange Routing Tables
        Synchronizing : Exchange Health Information
        Synchronizing : Synchronize Topology

        Synchronizing --> Federated

        Federated : Global Relay Federation Active

        Federated --> Synchronizing : Topology Changed
        Federated --> PeerLost : Peer Failure

        PeerLost : Remove Failed Peer

        PeerLost --> Synchronizing

    }

    Ready --> Federation : Federation Enabled
    Federation --> Ready : Federation Disabled

    %% =====================================================
    %% Failure Recovery
    %% =====================================================

    Failed : Relay Unavailable
    Failed : Await Recovery

    Failed --> Restarting : Automatic Recovery

    Restarting : Restart Relay Components
    Restarting : Restore Routing State

    Restarting --> Starting

    %% =====================================================
    %% Shutdown
    %% =====================================================

    Ready --> ShuttingDown : Shutdown Requested
    Federation --> ShuttingDown : Shutdown Requested

    ShuttingDown : Stop Accepting Connections
    ShuttingDown : Drain Active Sessions
    ShuttingDown : Flush Metrics
    ShuttingDown : Close Connections

    ShuttingDown --> Terminated

    Terminated : Relay Offline

    Terminated --> [*]

    %% =====================================================
    %% Global Failure Paths
    %% =====================================================

    Authenticating --> Failed : Internal Error
    Routing --> Failed : Routing Engine Failure
    Monitoring --> Failed : Health Monitor Failure
    Initializing --> Failed : Startup Failure